profile:
Absolute Home Services is a one stop shop for all of your home services. We currently specialize in:
 
1. Interior and Exterior Painting
2. Handyman Services
3. Lawn and Garden Maintenance
4. Landscaping
5. Interlock

 
Please contact us through email, website or phone call. The PING messaging service does not work well for communication purposes.
 
Customer satisfaction and retention is our primary focus. Therefore, we will do whatever it takes to ensure you are happy with our quality and service. Our goal is to have a customer for life! We want you to use us for all of our services, so we ensure you are happy after each service you use.
 
We service:
 
Mississauga, Oakville, Burlington, Hamilton, Milton, Toronto, Vaughan, Aurora, Newmarket, Barrie and Muskoka
 
We work on both commercial and residential projects.
 
Whether we are landscaping or painting, we have experienced people in each of their trades. Our painters take pride in what they do and are passionate providing high quality paint jobs. We have experts in interlock, lawn care and garden services who will give you the advice you need and a professional job.
 
Our service is what sets us a part from the rest. We have great people to provide great quality work, but we also have a goal to retain our customers for multiple services. In order to achieve this goal, we need to provide clear expectations, detailed quotes, communicate and deliver what we promise.
service_area: We service the GTA including Hamilton, Burlington, Oakville, MIlton, Mississsauga, Etobicoke, Barrie, Newmarket, Aurora, Vaughan and Muskoka areas. We will also service Toronto for some of services. We don't service Toronto for lawn cutting and gardening unfortunately.
products:
We only use top of the line products for paint, soil and concrete products. We work with our suppliers to get the best rates and service so that we can pass it along to you. We will use any product you like, but we have great relationships with the following suppliers:
1. Dulux Paints
2. Sherwin Williams Paints
3. Benjamin Moore Paints
4. Muskoka Lumber
5. Connon's Nursaries
6. Burlington Garden Supplies
7. Cap-Brick

services:
We provide services residential and commercial properties.

We offer the following services in each category:
1. Interior painting-Walls, trim, ceilings, kitchen cabinet spraying and                       staircase refinishing, drywall and drywall repair
2. Exterior painting-Soffits, windows, wood, vinyl and aluminum siding, doors, decks and fences
3. Lawn maintenance-lawn cutting,gardening, fertilizing, weed control, overseeding, aerating, spring and fall clean up and sodding
4. Landscaping-Interlock and planting
5. Handyman Services-stone veneer, backsplash, baseboards, laminate flooring, drywall and more.

We are also happy to clean your windows and steam clean your ceramic tiles and grout

profile:
Pro-Loc Interlocking & Landscape Design is a privately owned company established in 2003. 
With an early focus on residential interlocking and landscaping contracts, Pro-Loc has matured into a full service residential and commercial interlocking company with expertise spanning all aspects of large-scale project disciplines. 
Today, we successfully manage commercial and residential interlocking and landscape design projects all across southern Ontario.

Pro-Loc Interlocking & Landscape Design is a multi-craft employer providing a wide variety of services ranging from individual turnkey installations to large-scale specialty subcontracting assignments including Interlock Paver Installation. 

When schedules matter, we offer a competitive advantage you can count on. We provide outstanding "backstage" support to our field operations helping projects run smoothly. 
In the field, we maintain a steady workforce of skilled craftsmen and project managers allowing projects to progress smoothly to completion.

Our craftsmen take great pride in both the quality of their work and the aesthetic beauty of the finished product. 

We are open for business and we are following all Covid-19 regulations.

profile:
We are a proffesional Design and Build Landscape Contractor.  We service the Western Toronto, From Etobicoke to Hamilton and beyond.  We take pride in the work we do, and spend time with each an every potential client to ensure the final outcome meets their expectations.  We are not your discount Landscaper, we are meticulous, and set high standards for ourselves.

We have Finished carpenters on staff, so consider us your one stop shop for all your outdoor needs, from decks to interlock patio's, flagstone, to complete outdoor (12v) lighting systems.

Lou'ay & Mark

profile:
Singular Focus:

Most landscape and renovation companies try to serve many types of customers at the same time; homeowners, shopping centers, office buildings, golf courses, and the list goes on. They are pulled in all directions trying to be everything to everyone. At Captain Handy Co, we focus on one customer, you, the homeowner. We have a singular focus on bringing you the best landscaping and interior renovation, the best customer service, and the best value for your home. When you consider that quality renovation can improve the value of your home by 10%-15%, why wouldn’t you hire the one company that focuses specifically on residential landscaping? We are Your Residential Landscape and interior renovation Company.
Easy:

Our business makes your life easier. We are committed to improving the quality of life for our customers so they can spend their time on other things. Our customers are busy and have hectic lives. They do not have time to deal with different companies for lawn care, mowing, design, patio building. Captain Handy Co. offers turn-key solutions to your landscape needs. One call connects you with one of our very qualified Landscape Advisors who will make sure that you are delighted with your landscape. It is that easy.
Hassle-Free:

Ever notice how some companies make it a hassle just to do business with them? Who needs hassles? Life is complicated enough as it is. With Captain Handy Co, you can expect fast response times, clear and concise proposals, and work to be done how and when we promise it would be. You can also expect us to stand behind our work, show up when we say we will and take care of the little things that can take a landscape,renovation and experience, from blah to wow! We take away the hassles so all you have to do is enjoy your landscape.
Professional:

With 5 years under our belts, we know a thing or two about being the professional contractor of choice. Our staff has an average tenure rate of over twelve years, and some team members have been with us for over two decades! They undergo extensive and on-going training to not only assure that your renovation looks fantastic, but also to make sure that you are treated superbly. Our staff members are clearly recognizable in their sharp uniforms so you will know who is on your property. With so many companies claiming to be “professional”, isn’t it nice to work with a company that actually is?
Our Values:

At Captain Handy Co, we provide Tender Loving Care to both you and your interior and landscape renovation. These are our Values:
•	Treat people honestly, fairly and with respect in all situations
•	Create a comfortable environment in which to work and do business
•	Be open to problems and complaints, and work quickly to a fair resolution
•	Present a professional image and working safely
•	Have a “can-do” attitude
•	Stand behind our commitment to quality and service
•	Be active, responsible and positive citizens in the communities in which we work

profile: ROYAL Decks Co. is a custom decking company priding itself in high quality of work and complete customer satisfaction. ROYAL Decks Co. focuses on specialty materials, such as exotic hardwoods, low maintenance materials and high grades of cedar. ROYAL Decks Co. offers a complete solution for a homeowner from custom designs to the execution of the project. ROYAL Decks Co. was founded in Burlington Ontario and quickly grew to serve all surrounding areas of Toronto and also Calgary since 2008 onwards. We are successful because we take every deck builder project as if it was the only one, although we build hundreds each year. Our success is based on the following five core values: Great design Quality work Build on time and budget Provide great warranty Safety Great design In order for the deck to be great, it has to be usable, look great and fulfill all of the customer's expectations. With our extensive experience, we will work with you to design the deck that will serve the purpose, according to your needs. This means getting the right size and shape of the deck, getting the right features and selecting the right materials. We work with many materials of different properties and we are sure to find one that will work for you. Build quality We have only the most experienced carpenters. Our carpenters have been in construction most of their lives and they build decks not because they have to, but because they love it. All of our decks have to meet very strict ROYAL Decks Co. quality control on top of any building code requirements. Our decks not only meet building code, they exceed it. Build on time and on budget Our estimate includes time frame when the project will be started, how long it will take and how much exactly it will cost. We strive to make the construction process an enjoyable experience. That is why we take these extra seriously. Provide great warranty We are proud to give one of the best warranties in the business to every deck that carries ROYAL Decks Co. name on it. We stand behind the work that we do. To see details about our warranty please visit our warranty website. Safety Safety is our utter most requirement doing any work. We carry both WCB and WSIB, to date without a single claim. We keep our workplace neat and organized to minimize any injuries. Sincerely, Miro

profile:
Enviro-Loc Interlocking Ltd. is a privately owned company with over 15 years of experience in the Interlocking and Landscaping industry.  Based out of Milton, Ontario, we are happy to service the West GTA.

Enviro-Loc Interlocking Ltd. is a full-service luxury landscape company with staff that are trained in up to date industry leading practices.  We onboard our teams to instil our company’s expectations of excellence.  The staff go through weekly training sessions to ensure our sales representatives, office admin and skilled labourers have an in depth understanding of their responsibilities to you, the customer.

At Enviro-Loc Interlocking Ltd. we are truly committed to our customers throughout the entire job process.  We take all necessary steps to ensure an enjoyable experience from beginning to end.  We pride ourselves in our dedication to offering the best solution for your driveway, patio and front entrance and in maintaining a premium level of customer service. 

At Enviro-Loc Interlocking Ltd. we have 2 core values; our Customers and the Environment. Not only do we offer the best quality products and services, we are also committed to minimizing our carbon footprint.  We are proud to be the front runners in taking an environmentally friendly approach to a very polluted industry. 

Enviro-Loc Interlocking Ltd. is fully licensed, bonded and insured.  We are equipped with Worker’s Compensation (WSIB) and a $2,000,000 liability insurance policy protecting your personal assets.   Our work is protected by a written two year workmanship warranty that covers all aspects of the project.  All of the products we use are covered by a lifetime guarantee through Canadian based manufacturers.

At Enviro-Loc Interlocking Ltd. we are aiming to innovate the interlocking industry.  We are committed to lead our industry towards a future that is not only cleaner, but is also more environmentally responsible. We take pride in building a better tomorrow for future generations.

profile:
Winner of many awards including a national and provincial award for best residential design. With passion and creativity and over twenty years' experience in beautifying properties all over the GTA, Land-Con prides itself on customer satisfaction and customer experience before, during and after the project is completed. We are very honest with our customers, keeping them up to date regularly with the progress of the project. We strive to give our customers the highest quality of work, starting with our very experienced in house, award winning landscape designers, as well as extremely professional and respectable trade personal on the job site, with the owners them selves over seeing every single project on a daily basis.
We have received industry wide recognition for design and build, professionalism and customer satisfaction.


ACCOMPLISHED TEAM
Active Member of Landscape Ontario and Bild.  ICPI and NCMA certified.  Techno-Bloc Pro installer.  Permacon Pro installer.  2016 Winner of 2 Landscape Awards of Excellence, 2017 winner of 3 landscape awards of excellence, 2019 National Award, 2020 Winner of 3 landscape awards of excellence and the Van Casey award for best Design. 
At Land-Con, our principles, passion and reputation speak for themselves.  Our valued clients will agree; excellence in project management, coupled with our highly qualified management and crew are second to none.


COMPASSIONATE CARE
We build to capture and reflect the unique vision our clients trust us to create while abiding to strict standards and timelines.  We value your expectations and opinion and respect the importance of budget guidelines.  The job site will always be left cleaned up and tidy and ready for next day construction.  We respect your property and will be courteous and considerate of you and your neighbors.


AFTER CARE
At Land-con we believe that after a project is completed the aftercare with our customers is just as important as any part of the project.  If at any time after the project is completed, you have any questions or concerns we are here to help.  We back our workmanship with a five year extended warranty.  This warranty is transferable if you happen to sell your home within the five year period.  Our top priority is customer service. profile:
Since we started serving the GTA in 2006 we have been dedicated to providing the ultimate finished product. We specialize in residential and commercial landscaping including Re/Re work such as trench and boulevard restoration. All of our work is designed to not only be aesthetically pleasing but also withstand the harsh Canadian climate. We also provide a complete property maintenance service for condo complexes, plazas, and residential. The end goal is to provide the best quality service to our clients. 

All jobs are fully insured and bonded. 

**

We provide helpful suggestions and create beautiful custom designs suitable for any budget. The sales representative's job isn't over after the contract is signed, they are there to help throughout the process, ready to answer any questions you might have and handle changes at the customers request in a professional and timely manner. Daily updates on how the project is going are provided to ensure that everything has been completed to our customers needs. We warranty all of our work. Our plan is to make sure that all of our customers enjoy working with us and enjoy their new outdoor space. 

**

Please contact us and we would be happy to send a sales representative out for a free quote with no obligation.

profile:
Outdoor Lighting Perspectives is the world's largest full-service outdoor lighting company, and we are proud to have our fixtures enjoyed at more than 150,000+ homes across North America. 

Whatever your outdoor lighting needs, we have the experience and expertise to get it done right the first time.

WHAT WE DO:

We want to transform your outdoor living spaces in the best way possible. Some of our exquisite outdoor lighting options include:

-Accent lighting to subtly show off your property’s best features
-Architectural lighting to highlight your home’s unique beauty
-Pool lighting to keep your nightly swims safe
-Patio and deck lights to add excitement to your nighttime entertaining
-Garden lighting to accentuate your stunning landscaping
-Path lighting to guide your guests where they need to go
-Up-lighting for home facade, trees, and outdoor artwork

From a single small garden that needs just a touch of light, to a sprawling estate home that needs lighting with zone control automation, we offer it all.

Call us today for a free at-home consultation, and one of our lighting designers will make a customs lighting design for your unique property.

WHAT MAKES US DIFFERENT:

We are dedicated outdoor lighting designers and installers. We do one thing, and we do it the best. We aren't a sprinkler company or lawn care company moonlighting in outdoor lights when times are slow. We will be here to take the call when your lights need maintenance years down the road.

We manufacture our lights by hand, mostly in the United States but some right here in Toronto, so we can control the entire chain of quality from raw materials to your beautiful garden. 

Our designers, installers, and service crews are all our own staff: we do not use sub-contractors. With Outdoor Lighting Perspectives, your satisfaction is guaranteed in writing and backed by our 30 year on-site warranty.

THE TRUSTWORTHY CHOICE:

How can you find an outdoor lighting contractor you can trust to get the work done right, on time, and safely? 

We have been independently vetted by a third-party for our complete and up-to-date liability insurance and workers compensation coverage, our safety and training compliance, and our long established track record of happy customer referrals and testimonials. 

Companies claiming to do lighting come and go, but we're celebrating 20 years and our warranty is backed by our international network of 60+ locations. We'll install your lights today, but we'll also maintain them for years to come.

THE NEXT STEP:

We offer free design consultations and free quotes. Please contact us to discuss your outdoor lighting needs and how we can be of assistance.

profile: In 2007, Green FX Landscaping was founded by Pino and Rob Arpa and began services the following spring. Since then, Green FX Landscaping has continued to provide exceptional, complete lawn maintenance for residential and commercial properties.  The knowledgeable technicians at Green FX Landscaping are made up of passionate people, each having years of experience in lawn and garden maintenance, new lawn installation (hydro seeding, terraseeding and sodding), and landscape management.  Building long-lasting and trusting relationships with our customers is very important to us and we strive to provide our clients with exceptional customer service and satisfaction. We take the time to get to know each of our clients so that we can better understand their vision and goals for their project to provide stunning results!  At Green FX Landscaping, your landscape is not only a representation of you but it is also a reflection of us; so you can take comfort in the fact that pride, precision, and hard work goes into every project.  Whether your property needs are residential or commercial, we will work with you to create the perfect lawn treatment plan that compliments your style and budget while protecting your investment and preserving the environment.

profile:
Design Turf has a 20-year history of selling ProGreen artificial grass products in the GTA and beyond. Our residential grass series has a brown fiber thatch producing a realistic looking grass and is 33% cooler than conventional turf. Plus, with the new patent-pending ProFlow backing that increases the drainage rate by approximately 400% and our moisture resistant fibers, the turf will be cleaner, drier and free from any unpleasant pet odors. Design Turf is also recognized for offering the highest quality of golf green products & for their professional installations. Design Turf golf greens are priced at $30/ft²+HST for full installation. A small 12’x15’, 2 hole backyard golf green can be as little as $7500+HST complete! 
 
Our most popular selling landscape turf averages $19/ft²+HST for full installation. All our turf is pet friendly and has excellent drainage! 
 
ProGreen manufacturing is the only North American artificial grass manufacturer to produce their products under one roof from start to finish. Our products are certifiably 100% LEAD & HEAVY METAL FREE!  ProGreen products have a life expectancy of 30-40 years, even under the harshest of conditions, including the play of multiple dogs or when used by busy daycare centers!
 
For the Do-It-Yourselfer
Design Turf’s price on Natural Prime 50 for supply only is just $6.20/ft²+HST (remember it supplied only and the rolls are 15' wide!). Find out how to install it yourself here!
 
Please contact us! Provide a daytime phone number, email address and street address, we ’ll be happy to show you samples and arrange a free quotation.

profile:
Bestloc Interlocking is trusted and respected landscape design and Installation company operating in the Greater Toronto and Surrounding Areas. As a proud and certified member of ICPI (Interlocking and Concrete Pavement Institute), we provide our clients with award winning landscape designs and industry leading installations. Bestloc was found on two main principles of encouraging family outdoor living and building structures that last.

Many years ago, Ryan Morant, founder and president started out being a labourer, where he developed his passion for the trade. He then became a foreman, and inspector, and subsequently a teacher. Under his leadership, our professional team of highly skilled and qualified personnel provides innovative landscape designs. With over 15 years of planting and masonry experience, and hundreds of thousands of square feet laid, Bestloc Interlocking embodies the values of strength, performance, and passion. We are dedicated to providing our clients with custom landscaping solutions.

We are in constant communication with our friends at ICPI (Interlocking and Concrete Pavement Institute), and are always up-to-date on industry leading techniques on landscape designs and installations. We offer good communication with our clients from the beginning of each project to its completion. Our experienced project management means your project is completed on time and on budget.

Furthermore, we complete every task with a commitment to integrity and a devotion to excellence using the best quality products guaranteed to leave a lasting impression. If you wish to create the finest outdoor living experience for you and your family, please do not hesitate to contact Bestloc Interlocking for a free consultation/estimate.

We started our Landscape and Interlocking Stone business in 1994 based on three pillars:  Integrity, Quality, and Service.

ONE job at a time… Unlike many other businesses we do ONE job at a time. It is important to us to be able to focus all our efforts into each customer so that they get the best in personal attention and their project is completed as expected and on time.

No Sub-Contracted Work…   We do all the work ourselves. Our employees are highly qualified, talented, and honest. We wouldn’t trust your project and our reputation to anyone else.

We deliver what we promise to do. We carry out our work according to what our customers want and expect. We strive to deliver the best results at the least possible cost for the client.
Our work exceeds construction standards and client’s expectations. We take satisfaction in showing our customers how their project is been done so that they may appreciate the workmanship that goes into their project.

As a Landscape Contractor and Designer....
Our Goal… To exceed the expectations of every client by doing our work with Honesty, Quality, and Professionalism.                                  
Our approach… We first listen to what our clients want and make suggestions based on that and our experience. We then proceed to work in an efficient and flexible manner through every phase of the project to suit the client's needs.
 
We are happy to provide you with the following services and more:
Patios, walkways, steps, porches, verandas, pergolas, driveways, flower beds, gardens, planting, sprinklers, lighting, stone BBQs, stone fireplaces, and much more.

Letter from Danilo Otero, owner of Royal Town Landscape Development, March 2012:

Dear Customers,

I would like to thank you and congratulate you for helping children in Nicaragua go to school. Because of you, we were able to provide school supplies to 100 kids this past month and we are already working to provide another one hundred sets of school supplies this Summer. 

Thank You!  You made a big difference.

Regards,

Danilo

profile:
Our mission is to enhance lifestyles by providing aesthetically appealing home and property improvements with professional care and quality. Hardscape Interlock Design thrives to being nationally recognized as revolutionizing the paving and outdoor lifestyle industry by becoming the preferred choice. We are deeply committed to maintaining the industry’s highest standards of customer service and support. We listen to our customer needs and strive everyday to earn the credibility that has been associated with our company name and operations since we began.
Whether you’re looking for high-quality, durable driveways or planning to design an outdoor retreat with interlocking paving stones, choose Hardscapes Specialists to do the job. While being recognized for our high quality of work, Hardscapes is committed to providing you with great customer service. Our experts look to cut no corners and are determined to not only meet, but exceed your all expectations. With our dynamic designs and superior customer service, we are certain that you’ll be ecstatic with the outcome of the project

Having a hard time constructing a unique design for your home? Not a problem- Hardscapes Sales representatives have between 5-10 years of skilled and creative installation experience in the industry. They are also trained to help you construct exceptional quality and aesthetically beautiful designs to meet all your outdoor desires. If your still having trouble envisioning the outcome of your project, Hardscapes also offers a rendered design of your home to help you reach beyond your imagination and help visualize the final product. At Hardscapes, we have the experience and the knowledge to take your vision and make it into a reality. We plan on making your home the talk of the neighbourhood!
Hardscapes takes pride on our quality of work, while also being respectful to your neighbours by maintaining a clean and hazard free environment for the duration of the job. We guarantee that you will work with the same employees to oversee your project from concepts to its completion. Our paving stone installers are professional, respectful, fast and reliable. While many of our competitors leave projects incomplete and return to them at a later date, we are committed to concentrating on your job from start to finish, before moving onto another project. We are a design company full of innovative ideas and dedicated staff.

profile:
Ontario Green Irrigation is the company to service your irrigation needs in the GTA and the surrounding areas. Our mission is to beautify residential properties through quality lawn and shrub irrigation.
At Ontario Green Irrigation, we take pride in serving our customers. It's our desire to exceed your expectations in every way. We’d love to hear from you anytime. Contact us by phone or complete our online form and someone will be in touch with you to answer any questions or hear any suggestions you might have. 
We build irrigation systems that conserve water and automate the process of caring for lawns. Very little needs to be done on the part of our clients to achieve a healthy landscape. We coordinate with the town, take all necessary measurements and arrange for a licensed plumber to complete the hook-up with your plumbing system. Our state of the art equipment allows us to be efficient and available at all times. It also allows us to spend more time getting to know the needs of each particular lawn and customize the system accordingly.  
We are trained and experienced professional irrigation contractors with a history of customer satisfaction in both system installation and service We will select the right Rain Bird products for the unique needs of your landscape, program your controlled to operate at maximum efficiency, and instruct you on how to adjust your system's watering schedule to meet seasonal requirements.
service_area: Brampton, Mississauga, Etobicoke, North York, King City, Nobleton, Gormley, Markham, Vaughan, Toronto, GTA,
products:
We carry full lines of the most popular and good qualtiy sprinkler brands of Rotors, Spray heads, Electric Valves, Controllers, Drip Irrigation, Rain Sensors, etc. As a Rainbird Select Contractor we will install quality irrigation systems with genuine Rain Bird products.
Ontario Green Irrigation proudly uses almost exclusively Hunter and Rainbird Irrigation Products. Hunter and Rainbird products are known as the "Cadillac" of the industry and include a complete lines of sprinklers, rotary heads, shrub heads, valves, controllers (timers) and a variety of accessory products, including rain sensors. Many Hunter and Rainbird products are guaranteed for up to 5 years and can be replaced for labor costs only in the event of failure.
Rotary Sprinkler Rotor-type sprinklers have one or more moving streams of water that rotate around the sprinkler head.
Spray Sprinkler Spray-type sprinklers spray a fan of water out of the nozzle, similar to a shower head.
Valves Electric solenoid valves used for turning on irrigation circuits (sprinklers or drip emitters.) Includes anti-siphon, angle, and globe type valves.
Controllers Controllers are fancy timers used to turn on and off automatic valves.
services:
REPAIR ALL BRANDS OF LAWN SPRINKLERS QUICKLY AND PROPERLY.
Our service techs are experienced and well-trained, and our service trucks are equipped with the latest troubleshooting equipment which allows us to quickly diagnose, troubleshoot, and properly repair all brands of sprinkler systems.
RE-ROUTING A SPRINKLER SYSTEM during swimming pool construction is no problem for Fellows Irrigation. We will cap off existing irrigation to permit usage of lawn sprinklers in areas not affected by construction, then re-route sprinklers around pool as needed to maintain a beautiful backyard.
INSTALL NEW LAWN SPRINKLERS SYSTEM - Ontario Green Irrigation will custom-design and install your system to give the most efficient, cost effective lawn sprinkler possible. Zone landscape areas to water according to watering needs. Landscape areas in full shade (between houses, for example) need less water than full sun areas. Proper zoning of your system will cost more to install but save you money in the future as well as save our most precious resource - water!
QUALITY PRODUCTS COMBINED WITH SKILLED SERVICE TECHS is what Ontario Green Irrigation is about and what will make you a satisfied customer.

profile: At AquaSpa Pools we believe that a pool and its surrounding landscape is more than just a home improvement. It is an exciting new lifestyle. Quality pool and landsacping design increases the value and beauty of your property, brings tranquility and enjoyment to your backyard and is an expression of who you are. As every person and family is different, so is every project. Your backyard retreat will be customized to suit your individual needs and bring your dream surroundings to life. From inviting pools and spas, to flagstone paths and rejuvenating gardens, we treat every project as if it were our own home. DESIGN Our certified pool and landscape designers will listen to your ideas and wishes, and offer their experienced input. Then they will visualize your dream space, using the latest CAD design programs and hand-drawn renderings. QUALITY AquaSpa Pools & Landscape Design uses only the best construction materials, combined with experienced quality workmanship. Our knowledge of proper construction techniques will give you years of trouble-free enjoyment. TIMELINES We constantly amaze our clients with the speed in which we complete our projects. We go to great lengths to ensure that projects stay on schedule and that the final results surpass all expectations. WARRANTY We partner with the best equipment suppliers in the industry to provide our clients with premium products and comprehensive manufacturer warranties. AquaSpa Pools & Landscape Design stands by all of the work that we do, making the enjoyment of your new backyard retreat worry-free. SERVICE At AquaSpa we not only design and build your pool and landscaping, we also provide reliable after-service. Our familiarity with your unique project and our trained staff's knowledge of the equipment used will ensure efficient service and maintenance. After-services include pool opening and closing, safety cover installations, liner replacement and more. ENVIRONMENTAL RESPONSIBILITY Our pools use intelligent multispeed pumps and 2" plumbing to reduce electrical consumption, increase efficiency and pass savings along to you,. Cartridge style filters are used to avoid wasting water during backwashes, not to mention conforming to City by-law reference sewer use. Using safe water systems eliminates the need for harsh chemicals and the pollution associated with the production, packaging and transportation of these dangerous materials. Option R value insulation is used behind the steel panels and in the plumbing trenches to reduce the loss of heat. SPECIALIZING IN Pools, Spas, Hot Tubs, Water Features, Infinity Edge, Landscaping, Patios, Cabanas, Gazebos, Outdoor Kitchens & Fireplaces OUR PROFESSIONAL SERVICES INCLUDE: Renovations/Upgrades, Salt Water Conversions, Liner Replacement/Repair, Opening/Closings, General Repairs, Inspections, Safety Cover Installation ACCESSORIES Automatic Pool Cleaners, Pool Covers, Automatic Pool Covers, Fitness Swim Jets, Outdoor Lighting, Pool Controls, Water Accents, Salt Systems, Solar Systems

profile:
Filedmasters Synthetic Grass is second to none in the synthetic turf industry. Since 1991 we have provided the Canadian market with high-quality artificial turf products that are ideal for putting or golf greens, playgrounds, landscaping and more. 

Due to increasing water shortages and environmental concerns regarding chemicals and lawn fertilizers, more homeowners, business owners, and city governments are opting to install our products. Our synthetic grass eliminates the need for constant maintenance such as irrigation, mowing, fertilizing, aerating and more.

Fieldmasters products are durable, versatile, safe, economical and 100% recyclable. Most importantly, they look and feel so much like real natural sod that they enhance the look of any residential or commercial landscape. We are proud to offer our clients a high-quality product that will stand the test of time.

We also offer ull landscape and design for residential, recreational and commercial properties.

Residential: Grass replacement (back yard, front yard, balconies, roof tops), pool deck covering, interlocking patios, retaining walls, fencing, path ways and flag stones. 

Recreational: Sports fields such as soccer, football, lacrosse and lawn bowling.

Commercial: Day cares, community centers,  dog kennels, dog spas, gold centers, fitness centers.

....and many more!

- We are proudly Canadian
- We are located in GTA, in turn can provide quick response as required
- Proven success various of installation (installers are certified)
- Our product is North American made from one of the largest artificial turf manufacturer in the world. They are leaders in manufacturing artificial turf for various uses, industries and geographic locations
- We’ve been in business for 25+ years.
- Our turf is technologically advanced synthetic turf system that is engineered for durability, performance, and appearance
- Our backing is a premium design/quality, resulting in better drainage, better suited for pet management and weed prevention
- Our product is 100% made from new materials, no part of the turf is recycled or has been used previously
- Our product is 100% recyclable, heaven forbid you wanted to remove it
- Our product is 100% lead free and fire tested (have certifications to prove it)
- Our product doesn’t attract insects, animals won’t eat it, weed will not grow through it,  it’s allergen-free, and accidents wash right through
- Our product is designed to deter against various elements: high human and non-human traffic, heavy rain, heavy snow, high winds, high sun
- 10 year limited warranty
- Fully insured and WSIB
- Many references (see the pictures for a small sample of what we have accomplished)

Welcome to Empire Property Services Inc. 

Interlocking Stone and Retaining Walls: We offer repair on existing interlock pavers involving taking up interlock pavers and cleaning them and re level the base,  lay new screening and re lay existing pavers.

*******************************

Landscaping Services for Residential: Property Maintenance, Gardening, Grass Cutting, Hedge Trimming, Garden Bed Mulching, Weed Control, Perennial and Annual Flower Planting. 

Irrigation spring start up and winterization shut down. 

We remove and regrade old lawns and lay new sod. We will focus on soil improvement by rototilling compost and peat moss into soil to improvie soil nutrient level. Top dress, seed and fertiliae lawns. 


Contact us today to schedule an appointment.

profile:
VP Landscape is more than just a company, it is years built on hard work, dedication and passion for the industry. In his younger years, owner, Vito lived in Sala Consilina in the province of Salerno, in Italy. In a town where agriculture and farming was a main source of income, Vito was always intrigued by landscaping. When he immigrated to Canada he began his journey in landscape where he worked alongside his brothers. VP Landscape was born when Vito decided it was time to chase his dreams and begin his very own landscaping company.

Today, you will see VP Landscape and their work in high-end, residential properties in and around the GTA. Vito, alongside his son, Michael work together to envision and then execute the unique designs that they imagine for each individual client. They pride themselves on their ability to respect client privacy during and upon completion of every project. Their speciality remains in formal and manicured properties in which their expertise and passion evidently shine through.

Many of the details that you see in their work have been inspired by gardens and landscapes all over the world. Their various style adaptability, outstanding attention to detail and family orientated nature makes them one of the most reputable and personable landscape companies in Canada.

profile:
Welcome to Simply Exquisite, we are a construction and renovations general contractor in Toronto, serving the GTA and surrounding areas.

For over 20 years we have worked with property and homeowners providing them with high caliber commercial and home renovation services. We have earned our reputation as one of the best general contractors in the GTA through our trade expertise and professionalism. We are customer-service driven, pay extra attention to details, and deliver a quality product, on time and budget.

We approach every project with this simply promise: Every home renovation, general contracting, and construction project will be Simply Exquisite. That is our guarantee.

Whether you are looking to do a home renovation in Toronto, from kitchen design and renovations, to bathroom remodels and basement finishing, or something smaller like having your kitchen refaced or installing basement heated flooring, you can trust the best construction company in Toronto to give you the peace of mind of a job well done.

We offer award-winning renovation services that come with a 5-year warranty. We provide in-house design services and counseling, free of charge, with a licensed architectural designer. We extend this added value with every one of our projects so that you can be sure that your project will satisfy your needs.

profile:
Since the spring of 2000, Simple Solutions Landscaping has been offering quality services year-round in the North York neighborhoods of Armour Heights, Bathurst Manor, Clanton Park, Bayview Village, Newtonbrook, and Willowdale. We are dedicated to treating our clients with friendly and personalized customer service.

Brian Withey of Simple Solutions Landscaping is an established North York, and Toronto based landscaping company. They offer quality services year-round, with a focus on customer service. 

Since 2000, we've been helping people like you to maintain and enjoy the outside of your property.

Whether you are looking for general landscaping services or a company that can handle sodding, lawn aerating, grass cutting, hedge trimming, seeding, lawn dethachment or other property maintenance jobs, Simple Solutions has got you covered.

We improve the value of your property by caring for your yard. A new garden or walkway improves the curb appeal of your home. We create custom plans to suit your needs.

In the winter, we are on call 24/7 to remove snow from your drive and walkways with an easy fixed monthly bill. We use quality snow removal equipment to clear the path so you can feel safe and relaxed all winter long.

Simple Solutions is dedicated to ensuring you're satisfied with the job, we welcome your phone calls and questions. Call us today for help with your landscaping or snow removal needs!

profile: We are a Toronto based full service landscaping, garden design and installation company with our own planting, stonework, woodwork crews and landscapers with a unique focus on quality of design, and integration of inside and outside living space. Inside and Out Garden Design has been creating beautiful, artistic and functional gardens throughout the Greater Toronto Area for twenty years. We are professionals, with backgrounds in architecture and the arts, skilled in horticulture, stonework and carpentry, and passionate about our work. We specialize in creating unity, harmony, and delight in your outdoor living area, and in making it useful and enjoyable for years to come. We have found creative ways to use fencing, trellises, arbors, decks, planting, patios, walkways, stone walls, garden structures, pools and water features to enhance the value and livability of your home. We also create container gardens and we can design and install green roofs. Our approach is designed to put your ideas into beautiful form We would love to meet with you to discuss your garden needs. Contact us! Our Services We offer a full range of design and installation services for gardens, from balconies to estates, including planting, woodwork, stonework, and water features. Consultation- Our first step is to meet with you and get to know your needs and aspirations for your garden. We look at the situation of your garden in relation to sun, privacy and views, access, drainage, existing plant materials and structures, and suggest possibilities for improvement or development in the context of your past experience with it, your own vision or objectives, and your budget. At this time, if you would like us to prepare a design drawing, we can tell you our design fee, which is based on the size and complexity of the project. Design- The first step in the design process is to measure and photograph your garden for reference. Based on our discussions with you, we then prepare a design, along with a ballpark cost estimate. Once these have been reviewed and any changes made, we can prepare a firm quotation for installation of each element. Installation- Once you decide to proceed, we can schedule the work in accordance with your needs. Structural elements such as stonework and woodwork are installed first. Drainage and soil preparation is extremely important, and we can augment your soil as necessary to support healthy plant growth. We also coordinate installation of lighting and irrigation. Following this, planting takes place (and this can be throughout the spring, summer or fall seasons for most plant materials). Care and Maintenance- Generally, most people are looking for a garden which provides maximum benefit with minimal maintenance. We design the garden with this in mind, and provide you with the knowledge to take care of it. At Inside & Out, gardens aren’t just a business, they’re a vocation. Whether the project is a single display planter or a full garden design and installation, the ultimate reward for our work is the satisfaction of bringing some of nature’s beauty and serenity into the lives of our clients. Also find us on Facebook http://www.facebook.com/InsideAndOutGardenDesign
service_area: Toronto, Mississauga, Scarborough and elsewhere in the GTA, and now providing landscape design services in Northumberland County, Ontario

profile:
Welcome to Beauty Landscape. Our company Beauty-Landscape we pride ourselves on being flexible, dependable, and committed to quality Here is some information about us:


Our reputation is rock solid

Why? At Beauty-Landscape, we pride ourselves on being flexible, dependable, and committed to quality:

Flexible

Whether we’re in your backyard or on your commercial construction site, we have the expertise to get the job done on time, on budget, and on trend.

Dependable

We handle every phase of your project – from planning and design to installation and construction. And since design, engineering and installation are all done in-house – stripping out the middleman and avoiding sub-contractors - you can be confident in our competitive pricing and high quality work.*

Committed to Quality

We firmly believe that our work is only as good as the products we use. That’s why the highest quality materials the industry has to offer are the standard at Beauty-Landscape.


Our Services:

Paver Repair
Repairs / Sealer
Sod installation
Spring / Fall Clean-Up
Walkway / Retaining Wall
Bush and Tree Trimming
Carpentry
Driveway
Fences & Decks
Interlocking and Flag Stone
Lawn Maintenance
Floor and Tiling


Feel free to ask any landscaping or gardening questions over the phone.

profile:
Established design/build landscaping company, celebrating our 25th year serving the western GTA. 

Our Mission:: 
Is to achieve our success through customer satisfaction. We offer a full range of landscape design & build services but at the same time focus on our strong points. We are able to achieve this by following our company tradition of working and completing only one project at a time. 

Our Passion:: 
There is more to landscaping than assembling a combination of stone, wood and plant material. Landscaping is inspiration, collaboration and community, it is being able to live your outdoor life and share it with neighbours, friends and family. 

Together we can make your outdoor dreams become a reality. 
For an appointment to review your landscape needs, contact us for a design consultation today. 

www.greenscapedesignbuild.ca 
greenscape@sympatico.ca

profile:
Simple Solution is helping families adjust their homes to better serve their needs.
If you require a professionally installed automatic sprinkler system to enhance growth to your lawn and protect your valuable plants and landscaping, an outstanding low voltage landscape lighting system to beautify and secure your home at night or pre/post wiring for network, audio or video Simple Solution is a right choice. All of our projects are built using quality parts and procedures, designed to last and provide you with comprehensive hassle free system. We also stand behind our products and work hard to deserve your loyalty by maintaining every system we install in a friendly and professional manner for years to come.
We are locally owned and operated and install only the highest quality of products. We work on all major brands.

Our areas of expertise include:
Low voltage LED outdoor lighting, design, and installation.
Pre wiring and post wiring (retrofit) for security systems, audio, video, network, television, telephone and cable.
Irrigation/Sprinkle System design, installation, repair, annual services, upgrades and additions.

We understand the value of time and money. We work closely with you, listen to your every question and concern to learn your tastes and incorporate your style to create your dream home. Our projects are on schedule and on budget.

Simple Solution has one of the lowest overhead rates in the business which enables us to offer lower rates.

Contact us for free advice and free on-site estimate.
